thread.title: TV | Valkyrie

author: Brian Lloyd
title: TV | Valkyrie
text: Tom Cruise stars as Nazi conspirator Claus von Stauffenberg who attempted to assassinate Hitler and bring an end to World War II from inside. Directed by Bryan Singer, it's got a pretty impressive cast, too - Kenneth Brannagh, Bill Nighy, Tom Wilkinson and Terence Stamp. If you like twisty conspiracy thrillers, this one's for you.
